title: Large 1bdrm 1bath - Reserved, Heated Parking Included
posting_body: ['1 BR/1 BA AVAILABLE OCTOBER 5TH', 'River Ridge Apartments is a fantastic place to call home!', 'Each apartment includes air conditioning, ceiling fans, a dishwasher, and spacious closets.', 'One underground, heated, reserved garage stall included!', ' Great perk with winter fast approaching!', ' Dining, shopping, nearby lakes, and easy highway access are convenient bonuses living at River Ridge Apartments.', 'Are you ready to make the move to River Ridge?', 'This 1 bedroom 1 bath apartment features large closets, a spacious floor plan, modern kitchen amenities, and a large walk out patio!', 'Please call our friendly staff today and schedule an appointment to come visit your awesome new home!', 'show contact info', 'Apply now here!', ' <URL>', 'LEASING INFORMATION:', 'Qualifications: You must have an income of 2 times the monthly rent, no criminal or eviction history and a credit score of 625 or above.', ' We are not accepting co-signers.', 'Security Deposit: $300', 'Application Fee: $40 per applicant', 'Utilities Included in Rent: Heat', 'Utilities not Included: Electricity, Water, Basic Trash, and Sewer', 'Pets: Cats allowed.', 'No dogs.', 'Pet Fees: $200 fee, plus additional $200 deposit, plus $25 monthly pet rent', 'Laundry:', 'On-Site coin operated Washers, Dryers', 'Smoking:  This is a Smoke-Free building']
